Paper is a minimalistic decentralized social platform built on:
- ENS, EFP, ECP for Ethereum integration
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Bun

Directory structure highlights:
- `src/app/`: Next.js App Router pages and API routes
  - `(feed)/`, `(title)/`, `api/`, `p/[post]/`, `u/[user]/`
- `src/components/`: React components organized by domain
  - `auth/`, `communities/`, `notifications/`, `menu/`, `post/`, `ui/`, `user/`, `web3/`
- `src/lib/`: Protocol and service integrations
- `src/utils/`: Utilities, helpers, and tests

Key technologies:
- Web3: ENS, EFP, ECP, Ethereum Identity Kit
- Ethereum: Wagmi, Viem
- UI/Styling: Tailwind CSS, Shadcn/UI, Framer Motion


